NOFUNS:	DS	1			;ZERO IF NO FUNCTIONS ACTIVE. SAVES TIME IN SIMPLE SEARCH
TEMP9:	DS	2			;GARBAGE COLLECTION TEMP TO CHAIN THROUGH PARAMETER BLOCKS
FUNACT:	DS	2			;COUNT OF ACTIVE FUNCTIONS
